title: 02/03/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 02/03/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show we talk to a couple NFL All Pro Players. The Niner's George Kittle joins us to discuss his experience at the Super Bowl last year. The Washington Football Team's Chase Young discusses how he thinks his former Head Coach Urban Meyer will fare in the NFL. And Brandon Hauffman of 24-7 Sports tells us why Alabama could have a generational recruiting class this year.
